#: includes/xln-tools.php:169
msgid ""
"This page provides tools to assist with migrating and cleaning up content "
"for the Literair Nederland block-based theme. Please review each tool's "
"description and use with extreme caution, especially the cleanup tool which "
"can delete content. Always ensure you have a backup before running any "
"migration or cleanup operations."
